This topic describes how to install and configure Sumo Logic Nozzle for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF).

##<a id='prereqs'></a>Prerequisites

Before you install the Sumo Logic Nozzle for PCF tile:

* You need to have a [Sumo Logic](https://www.sumologic.com/pricing/) account.
* You must also configure PCF as an [HTTP Source](https://help.sumologic.com/?cid=5084) in Sumo Logic. 

##<a id='create-tile'></a> Install and Configure the Tile


1. Click the newly added Sumo Logic Nozzle for PCF tile to access the configuration settings.

